    "「%@」に参加しました": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Joined “%@”"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「%@」のパスワードロックを解除します。現在のパスワードを入力してから実行してください。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Remove the password lock for “%@”. Enter the current password before proceeding."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「%@」の支出について何でも聞いてください。\n例: 「今月の食費は?」「先週いちばん多く使った日は?」": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ask anything about spending in “%@”.\nE.g. “How much did I spend on food this month?” “Which day last week did I spend the most?”"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「%@」を削除しますか?": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Delete “%@”?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「%@」を削除しますか？": {
      "localizations": {
