    "「%@」を開く": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Open “%@”"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「コーヒー 350 円」と話しかけるだけで支出を記録できます。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Just say “Coffee 350 yen” to record an expense."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「コーヒー 350 円を追加」のように自然言語で Claude に頼むと、Budgety に直接記録できます。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ask Claude in natural language, like “Add coffee for 350 yen,” to record directly into Budgety."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「今月」表示時に進捗バーで残額を可視化します。0 のまま保存すると予算なし扱い。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Shows the remaining amount as a progress bar in the \"This Month\" view. Saving it as 0 means no budget."
          }
        }
      }
    },
