    "月額・年額プランは自動更新サブスクリプションです。期間終了の24時間以上前に解約しない限り自動更新され、購入確定時に Apple ID へ請求されます。解約・管理は「設定 > Apple ID > サブスクリプション」から行えます。買い切りプランは一度のお支払いで永続します。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The monthly and yearly plans are auto-renewing subscriptions. They renew automatically unless canceled at least 24 hours before the end of the period, and your Apple ID is charged when the purchase is confirmed. You can cancel or manage them in Settings > Apple ID > Subscriptions. The one-time plan is a single purchase that lasts forever."
          }
        }
      }
